sub_title: Recruitment Partner @ Fortrea | Strategic Sourcing Expert
summary:
I am a Recruitment Partner at Fortrea, a global leader in clinical research and development solutions. I have a Master of Science in Business Administration from VU University Amsterdam, with a focus on Human Resources Management. I am passionate about sourcing and placing candidates for various positions in the Life Science, Food, and Chemical industry in Europe, the US, and Asia Pacific region. 

In my current and previous roles at Seuss+, Fortrea and Labcorp Drug Development, I have worked on multiple Executive, Regulatory Affairs, Quality, Medical, Marketing, Business Development, and Software roles, using Boolean search, X-Ray/Google/Bing Search, LinkedIn Recruiter platform, Xing, Custom Search engines, and more. I have also received multiple People Excellence awards for my performance and contribution. I enjoy building relationships with potential candidates, experts, and professionals from diverse backgrounds and roles. I am always eager to learn new skills and explore new opportunities in the recruitment field.
